'''Jorma Aalto''' (born 24 August 1957) is a Finnish [[skiing|skier]]. He competed in the men's 30 kilometre cross-country ski race at the [[1980 Winter Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/aa/jorma-aalto-1.html |title=Jorma Aalto Olympic Results |accessdate=28 November 2017}}</ref>
